title: 00-TB-002: MSI
extract_protocol_ch1: Surgically isolated colorectal cancers were immediately frozen in liquid nitrogen. Total RNA was extracted from cancer tissue using Trizol reagent (Invitrogen).
label_protocol_ch1: Approximately 8 ug of total RNA was processed to produce biotinylated cRNA targets.
data_processing: The simpleaffy package in R/Bioconductor was used to calculate MAS5.0 calls. These values are not normalized. Normalization was performed by quantile normalization with respect to a defined reference set.
contact_address: 6th floor, Centre for Medical Research,  Royal Melbourne Hospital,  Royal Parade

data_processing: The simpleaffy package in R/Bioconductor was used to calculate MAS5.0 calls. These values are not normalized. Normalization was performed by quantile normalization with respect to a defined reference set.
contact_address: 6th floor, Centre for Medical Research,  Royal Melbourne Hospital,  Royal Parade
